<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Tools on The Developer Log of lingyin</title><link>https://microtears.github.io/tool/</link><description>Recent content in Tools on The Developer Log of lingyin</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://microtears.github.io/tool/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Counter</title><link>https://microtears.github.io/tool/counter/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://microtears.github.io/tool/counter/</guid><description>&lt;div class="page"&gt;
 &lt;article class="post"&gt;
 &lt;div class="post-content"&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;
 这是一个简单的浏览器计数器页面。使用按钮调整数值，并自动保存到本地存储，刷新后仍可保留当前计数。
 &lt;/p&gt;

 &lt;div class="counter-card"&gt;
 &lt;div class="counter-value" id="counterValue" aria-live="polite"&gt;0&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="counter-buttons"&gt;
 &lt;button type="button" id="decrementButton" aria-label="减少计数"&gt;-&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;button type="button" id="resetButton" aria-label="重置计数"&gt;重置&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;button type="button" id="incrementButton" aria-label="增加计数"&gt;+&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;

 &lt;p&gt;支持键盘操作：使用方向键、+/- 以及 R 键修改计数。&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/article&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;script&gt;
 (() =&gt; {
 const storageKey = "counter-page-value";
 const valueEl = document.getElementById("counterValue");
 const decrementButton = document.getElementById("decrementButton");
 const resetButton = document.getElementById("resetButton");
 const incrementButton = document.getElementById("incrementButton");

 const parseValue = (value) =&gt; {
 const num = Number(value);
 return Number.isFinite(num) ? num : 0;
 };

 const loadValue = () =&gt; {
 try {
 const stored = window.localStorage.getItem(storageKey);
 return parseValue(stored);
 } catch (error) {
 return 0;
 }
 };

 const saveValue = (value) =&gt; {
 try {
 window.localStorage.setItem(storageKey, String(value));
 } catch (error) {
 // ignore storage errors
 }
 };

 let counter = loadValue();

 const render = () =&gt; {
 valueEl.textContent = String(counter);
 };

 const update = (next) =&gt; {
 counter = next;
 saveValue(counter);
 render();
 };

 decrementButton.addEventListener("click", () =&gt; update(counter - 1));
 incrementButton.addEventListener("click", () =&gt; update(counter + 1));
 resetButton.addEventListener("click", () =&gt; update(0));

 window.addEventListener("keydown", (event) =&gt; {
 if (event.target instanceof HTMLButtonElement || event.target instanceof HTMLInputElement) {
 return;
 }

 switch (event.key) {
 case "ArrowUp":
 case "+":
 case "=":
 update(counter + 1);
 event.preventDefault();
 break;
 case "ArrowDown":
 case "-":
 update(counter - 1);
 event.preventDefault();
 break;
 case "r":
 case "R":
 update(0);
 event.preventDefault();
 break;
 }
 });

 render();
 })();
&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;style&gt;
 .counter-card {
 display: flex;
 flex-direction: column;
 gap: 1rem;
 margin-top: 1.4rem;
 padding: 1.4rem;
 border: 1px solid #c7c7c7;
 border-radius: 16px;
 background: #f8f9ff;
 }

 .counter-value {
 font-size: 4rem;
 font-weight: 700;
 text-align: center;
 color: #202124;
 }

 .counter-buttons {
 display: grid;
 grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
 gap: 0.75rem;
 }

 .counter-buttons button {
 padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
 font-size: 1.1rem;
 font-weight: 600;
 border: 1px solid #a3c9ff;
 border-radius: 12px;
 background: white;
 color: #222;
 cursor: pointer;
 transition:
 transform 0.15s ease,
 background-color 0.15s ease;
 }

 .counter-buttons button:hover,
 .counter-buttons button:focus-visible {
 background: #e6f0ff;
 transform: translateY(-1px);
 }

 .counter-buttons button:active {
 transform: translateY(0);
 }

 @media (max-width: 520px) {
 .counter-card {
 padding: 1rem;
 }

 .counter-value {
 font-size: 3rem;
 }
 }
&lt;/style&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>